    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个架构图来对比两种Claude Code的扩展机制：自动触发的hooks和手动输入的slash commands。核心是想说明它们的触发方式和用户参与度的差异。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HOOKS",
        "COMMANDS",
        "User"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。所以一边是claude-organize这种自动整理文件的hook，另一边是像/enhance这样的斜杠命令？我需要把它们做成两个并排的子图？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HOOKS",
        "COMMANDS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，左右结构或者上下结构都可以。关键是每个子图内部要展示四个关键特征，形成流程关系。hook那边是全自动的，从触发到执行不需要用户介入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "H1",
        "H2",
        "H3",
        "H4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我设计HOOKS子图用蓝色系，四个节点串起来：Automatic triggers → File operations → Background process → No user interaction。这样体现无人值守的感觉。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HOOKS",
        "H1",
