      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，用#4A90E2这个蓝色。COMMANDS那边用金黄色#FFD700，形成强烈对比。那边四个节点是User initiated开头，最后Returns to user结尾，强调有人参与。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMMANDS",
